LECTOTYPE DESIGNATION: Reuter (1876) described
P. psalliodes
from Belfrage specimens taken in ‘‘Texas’’, but he did not indicate how many specimens he had before him. I have found seven specimens in three museums (23, 3♀ NHRS; 1♀ USNM; and 1♀ MZH)
